'''Justin Dix''' was a droid technician working on the set of [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. He made a cameo appearance as [[Dixon Just]] in ''Attack of the Clones''.

